
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
Your name that is playing with my name<br />
Trying to get it and to erase yours<br />
Your joy that is singing with my joy<br />
So they would fuse together</p>
<p>Your heart that is playing with my heart<br />
With a lot of luck, of passionate luck<br />
And then your hand that is holding mine<br />
And guiding me through the shadow to the sun</p>
<p>We don&#8217;t need complicated romances<br />
Like those of lovers in movies<br />
We don&#8217;t need to put on an act<br />
Luck is as I see it</p>
<p>Your name that is playing with my name<br />
Trying to get it and to erase yours<br />
Your joy that sings with my joy<br />
So that they would fuse together</p>
<p>Your heart that is playing with my heart<br />
With a lot of luck, of passionate luck<br />
And then your hand that is holding mine<br />
And guiding me through the shadow to the sun</p>
<p>To the sun<br />
